---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Digital Transformation Advisory"
  description="Digital Transformation Advisory for enterprise leaders. Design operating models that scale beyond the pilot and deliver measurable transformation outcomes."
>

  <section class="section-py bg-[#05070D]" aria-labelledby="dt-heading">
    <div class="container-site">

      <nav class="mb-8" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/advisory" class="text-white/40 text-sm hover:text-white/65 transition-colors">
          ← Advisory
        </a>
      </nav>

      <span class="eyebrow">Advisory · Digital Transformation</span>

      <h1 id="dt-heading" class="text-section font-heading font-bold text-white mt-2 mb-6 max-w-[20ch]">
        Digital Transformation Advisory
      </h1>

      <p class="text-white/65 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-[56ch] mb-6">
        Digital transformation programs consistently stall when strategy and operating model
        evolve at different speeds. As a Digital Transformation Advisor, I help enterprise
        organizations design and execute transformation programs that deliver measurable
        outcomes across people, process, technology and governance.
      </p>

      <p class="text-white/50 leading-relaxed max-w-[56ch] mb-12">
        The advisory covers operating model design, transformation program governance,
        portfolio alignment, execution discipline and the organizational change needed
        to sustain momentum beyond the initial pilot phase. Applied across banking,
        insurance, technology and product organizations.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">
          Book Advisory Call
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a href="/advisory" class="btn-outline">All Advisory Services</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
